hadiths[41]{hadithnumber,text}:
4227,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Faraa aur Ateera durust nahin.
4228,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Faraa aur Ateera sey mana farmaya hai.
4229,Hazrat Mikhnaf bin Sulem (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath arfa mein wuqoof kar rahey they ke aap ney farmaya : aey logo padhi. har ghar walon par eik saal baad qurbani bhi hai aur Ateera bhi. (raawi hadees) Muaz kehtey hain ke meri aakhon ney dekha ke ( Abdullah ) ibn Aun rajab mein Ateera ( janwer ) zibeh kartey they.
4230,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam sey riwayat hai ke logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Faraa key barey mein kya hukm hai? aap ney farmaya : ( Allah key naam par) theek hai lekin agar to usey ( zibeh karney ki bajaey) chhod dey (bada honey dey) yahan tak ke wo jawan oont ho jaey, phir to usey Allah Taala key raastey mein kisi ko sawari key liye dey ya kisi bewa ko dey dey to ye behtar hai us sey ke to usey (paida hotey hi) zibeh kar daley jabkey uska gosht uskey baalon hi sey laga ho, aur to apney (doodh key) bartan ko ondha kar dey aur apni oontni (us ki maa) ko bila wajah pareshan kerey. logon ney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool! Ateera? aap ney farmaya : Ateera bhi haq hai. ( wo bhi theek hai ). abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) ney farmaya : (raawi hadees) abu Ali hanfi (aur uskey bhai) wo chaar hain. un mein sey eik abu-Bakar hai, eik Bishr hai aur eik shareek hai, neez eik aur hai (uska naam Umer hai.)"
4231,Hazrat Haris bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajaatul-wadaa' mein mila. aap apni azbaa oontni par sawar they. main eik janib sey aap key paas hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! merey liye bakhshish ki dua farmaiye. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala tum sab ko maaf farmaey. phir main dusri janib sey aap key paas is ummid key sath aaya ke aap merey liye khususi dua farmaeyngey. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye bakhshish ki dua farmaiye. aap ney apney dono haath uthaey aur farmaya : Allah Taala tum sab ko maaf farmaey. logon mein sey eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Ateera aur Faraa' ka hukm kya hai? aap ney farmaya : jo chahey Ateera zibeh karey jo chahey na kerey. jo shakhs chahey Faraa' zibeh kerey. jo chahey na kerey. albatta bakriyon mein qurbani zaroori hai. aap ney ishara farmatey waqt apni sab ungliyan band kar lein magar eik khuli rakhi.
4232,"Hazrat Haris bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Hajjatul-wadaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko mila aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! merey liye bakhshish ki dua kijiye. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala tum sab ko maaf farmaey. us waqt aap apni oontni azbaa par sawar they, phir main dusri janib sey ghoom kar aaya. phir raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki."
4233,Hazrat Nabeesha (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas zikr kiya gaya ke hum zamanae-jahiliyat mein (maahe-Rajab mein) janwer zibeh kiya kartey they. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala key naam par zibeh karo jis mahiney mein bhi ho. Allah Taala key liye neki karo. aur (gharibon ko) khana khilaya karo.
4234,Hazrat Nabeesha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Mina mein baa-aawaaz buland kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum jahiliyat mein maahe-Rajab mein janwer zibeh kiya kartey they to aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ab hamein kya hukm detey hain? aap ney farmaya : jo bhi mahina ho ( Allah Taala key liye) zibeh karo. aur Allah Taala ki raza mandi key liye neki karo. aur (gharibon ko) khana khilaao. us aadmi ney kaha : hum Faraa' bhi zibeh kya kartey they. ab aap ka kya hukm hai? aap ney farmaya : har qism key charney waley janweron mein sey koi janwer zibeh karna chahiye (magar is tarah ke) bachchey ko uski maa doodh palaey yahan tak ke jab wo sawari key qabil ho jaey (pura oont ban jaey) to phir us ko zibeh kar aur us ka gosht sadqa kar.
4235,"Hazrat Nabeesha Hazli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tum ko teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht khaney sey roka tha taake sab log kha saken lekin Allah Taala ney soorate-haal behtar farma di hai. ab khao , sadqa karo aur zakhira kar key bhi rakh lo. ye (eid key) din khaney peeney aur Allah Taala key zikr key hain. eik aadmi ney kaha : hum zamanae-jahiliyat mein Rajab key doran mein janwer zibeh kiya karey they. ab aap ka kya hukm hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala key liye zibeh karo, jis mahiney mein bhi mumkin ho. aur khalis Allah Taala key liye neki karo aur (gharibon ko) khana khilaao. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum jahiliyat mein Faraa' bhi zibeh kiya kartey they. ab aap kya farmatey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : charney wali bakriyon mein sey koi bhi bakri zibeh kerni chahiye lekin (is tarah ke) to apni bakriyon mein rakh kar paaley-posey yahan tak ke jab wo jawan ho jaey to to usey zibeh kerey. phir us ka gosht musafiron waghera par sadqa kar dey. ye tariqa (jahiliyat ki rasm sey) badarjaha behtar hai."
4236,"Hazrat Nabeesha (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi ney baa-aawaaze buland Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pukar kar kaha : hum daure-jahiliyat mein maahe-Rajab key doran mein Ateera zibeh kiya kartey they. ab aap hamen kya hukm detey hain? aap ney farmaya : zibeh karo jis mahiney mein bhi ho. Allah Taala key liye neki karo aur logon ko khilaao. us ney kaha : hum jahiliyat mein Faraa' bhi zibeh kiya kartey they. aap ney farmaya : har charney waley janweron mein sey janwer zibeh karna chahiye lekin us waqt jab wo jawan ho jaey, phir to usey zibeh karey aur us ka gosht sadqa kar dey. yaqinan ye behtar hai."
4237,Hazrat Nabeesha Hazli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum jahiliyat mein Ateera zibeh kiya kartey they. ab aap ka kya hukm hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala key liye zibeh karo. jaunsa mahina bhi ho. Allah Taala (ki raza mandi key husool) key liye neki karo aur logon ko khana khilaao.
4238,"Hazrat Abu Rizeen Laqeet bin Aamir Aqeeli (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum daure-jahiliyat mein maahe-Rajab key doran mein kuch janwer zibeh kiya kartey they. hum khud bhi khatey they, apney paas aaney walon (aur milney milaaney walon) ko bhi khilatey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is mein koi harj nahin. (raawi hadees) Wakeea' bin Udus ney kaha : main to ye neki nahin chhodunga."
4239,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik murda bakri key paas sey guzrey jisey bahar phenk diya gaya tha. aap ney farmaya : ye kis ki hai? logon ney kaha : (Ummul-Mominin) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki. aap ney farmaya : agar wo iskey chamdey sey faeyda utha leti to kya harj hota? logon ney kaha : ye to murda hai. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney sirf iska (gosht waghera) khana haram kiya hai.
4240,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka guzar eik murdar bakri key paas sey huwa jo aap ney apni ehliya mohtarma Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki azad karda londi ko di thi, to (usey dekh kar) aap ney farmaya : tum ney iski khaal sey faeyda kyon nahin utha liya? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo to murdar hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : murdar (bakri) ka sirf khana haram kiya gaya hai."
4241,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (apni ehliya) Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki londi ki murdar bakri ko dekha jo sadqey key maal sey us ko di gaee thi. aap ney farmaya : agar wo iski khaal utaar letey aur phir is sey faeyda uthati to (behtar hota). unhoney kaha : wo to murdar hai. aap ney farmaya is ka sirf khana haram kiya gaya hai.
4242,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ney batlaya ke eik bakri mar gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ney uski khaal ko rang kyon nahin liya ke us sey faeyda uthatey?
4243,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka guzar Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki murdar bakri key paas sey huwa to aap ney farmaya : tum ney uski khaal ley kar usey rang kyon nahin liya ke us sey faeyda uthatey?
4244,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka guzar eik murdar bakri key paas sey huwa to aap ney farmaya : tum ney iski khaal sey faeyda kyon nahin utha liya?
4245,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mutahra (biwi) Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kiya ke hamari eik bakri mar gaee to hamney uski khaal ko rang liya, phir hum is mein nabeez banatey rahey yahan tak ke wo mushk bin gaee."
4246,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis kachchi khaal ko bhi rang liya jaey to wo pak ho jati hai."
4247,Hazrat ibn Wa'ala sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha ke hum un maghribi logon sey jang karney jatey hain jo ke but-parast hain. unkey paas mishkeezey hotey hain jin mein doodh ya pani hota hai. (to kya hum wo istimal kar saktey hain?) Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : dabaaghat chamdey ko pak kar deti hai. mainey kaha : ye aap ki raey hai ya aap ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai? unhoney farmaya : balke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai.
4248,Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah Taala key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-tabuk (key safar) main eik aurat key paas sey pani mangwaya. wo kehney lagi : merey paas pani to hai magar murdar key chamdey sey baney huye mishkeezey mein hai. aap ney farmaya : tu ney usey dabaaghat nahin di thi? us ney kaha : ji ! dabaaghat to di thi. aap ney farmaya : to dabaaghat (rangney) sey chamdaa pak ho jata hai.
4249,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey murdar key kachchey chamdey key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : dabaaghat (rangney) sey pak ho jata hai.
4250,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey murdar key chamdey key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : dabaaghat chamdey ko pak kar deti hai.
4251,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dabaaghat sey murdar ka chamdaa pak ho jata hai.
4252,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : murdar ka chamdaa dabaaghat sey pak ho jata hai.
4253,Hazrat Aaliya binte Sabee'a sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki Zauja mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ney mujhey bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey kuchh quraishi guzrey. wo apni eik mari hui bakri ko gadhey ki tarah ghaseet kar ley ja rahey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : agar tum is ka chamdaa utaar letey (to achchha). unhoney kaha : ye to mari hui hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : isey pani aur keekar ka chhilka pak kar deta hai.
4254,Hazrat Abdullah bin Akeem sey marwi hai ke main us waqt jawan ladka tha jab hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka khat padh kar sunaya gaya ke tum murdar key chamdey aur patthey sey faeyda na uthaao.
4255,Hazrat Abdullah bin Akeem sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein ye tehreer likh kar bheji : tum murdar key chamdey aur patthey sey faeyda na uthaao.
4256,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Akeem sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Juhaina qabiley ki taraf ye tehreer likh kar bheji : tum murdar key (baghair rangey) chamdey aur patthey ko istimal na karo. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : is masley mein sahih tareen riwayat wo hai jis mein dabaaghat sey chamdey key pak honey ka zikr hai, yani Zohri an Ubedullah, an ibne-Abbas, an Memuna wali riwayat. (Wallahu-Aalam)."
4257,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke jab murdar key chamdey ko rang diya jaey to us sey faeyda uthaya ja sakta hai.
4258,Hazrat Abul-Maleeh key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney darindon key chamdey istimal karney sey mana farmaya.
4259,"Hazrat Miqdaam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (mardon ko) resham, soney aur cheeton key chamdey sey baney huye gadelon key istimal sey mana farmaya hai."
4260,"Hazrat Khalid sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Miqdaam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : main aap sey Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya aap jantey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney darindon key chamdey pehan'ney aur un par sawar honey sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney farmaya : ji haan."
4261,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein farmatey suna : bilashuba Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sharab , murdar , khinzir aur buton ki kharid aur farokht sey mana farmaya hai. arz ki gaee : aey Allah key Rasool ! murdar ki charbi key barey mein kya hukm hai? ye kashtiyon ko mali jati hai aur chamdon ko lagai jati hai aur log us sey chiragh jalaatey hain? aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye haram hai. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney irshad farmaya : Allah Taala yahudiyon par lanat farmaai ke jab Allah Taala ney un par charbi ka istimal haram farmaya to unhoney charbi ko pighla kar bech diya aur uski qeemat khaney lagey."
4262,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye baat pahunchi ke Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ney Sharab bechi hai. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala Samura ko halak kerey. usey ilm nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai ke Allah Taala yahudiyon par lanat farmaee ke un par charbi haram hui to unhoney usey pighlaayaa (aur bech diya).
4263,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik chuhiyaa ghi mein giri aur mar gaee. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (us key mutalliq) sawal kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : chuhiyaa aur uskey ird-gird key ghi ko phenk do aur baqi kha lo.
4264,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya ke jamey huye ghi mein choohaa gir gaya hai. (usey kya kiya jaey?) aap ney farmaya : choohey aur uskey ird-gird key ghi ko nikal phenko.
4265,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : choohaa ghi mein gir jaey to (kya kiya jaey?) aap ney farmaya : agar (ghi) jama huwa ho to choohaa aur uskey ird-gird wala ghi bahar phenk do. (aur baqi ko istimal kar lo) lekin agar wo pighla huwa hai to uskey qarib bhi na jaao.
4266,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik murda bakri key paas sey guzrey. aap ney farmaya : agar is bakri key Malik iskey chamdey sey faeyda utha letey to kya harj tha?
4267,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi key (khaney peeney key) bartan mein makkhi gir jaey to usey dubo kar nikal diya jaey.
